& [InferenceJobResult] is outside preservation proposal
  + [focus] is worker local model reliability claim
  + [inside] is two successful isolated runs on one prompt family
  + [boundary] is rule that single prompt family does not generalize to all tasks
  + [outside] is unsupported claim of general reliability without broader testing
  + [inference] is limited evidence supports specific case only
  + [caution] is avoid extrapolating beyond tested prompts
  + [next_step] is conduct additional diverse prompt evaluations
